title: Amazing Stories
description:
The original "scientifiction" magazine started by Hugo Gernsback, Amazing Stories was the first magazine dedicated to that "ray-gun and outer space stuff" that vexed a generation of parents.

Filenames are harmonized with Carlo's list, and updates will maintain the same folder structure.

Please help seed this torrent and let others experience the fascinating world of early SF.

Key words: pulp, magazine, science fiction, Gernsback, Experimenter Publishing.
